15,01Love is blind
15,01and you,
15,01you, you offer up your heart
15,01so full of empty dreams
15,01Fold around yourself
15,01These dreams of love
15,01Blind as you are
15,01And you, you
15,01You are so perfect
15,01Only in my eyes
15,01Bound by the spider's golden webs
15,01Blind as I am
15,01The sun has stopped in our sky
15,01Clouds hover and
15,01Even the stars
15,01Hold their breath
15,01Blinded by the fury
15,01Of our heart's wings beating
15,01The love has consumed 
15,01All our fuel
15,01I fall into the blackness
15,01and my eyes
15,01Open.

15,01Forgiven 
15,01but not 
15,01Forgotten.

